msgid "A crisp red apple known for its refreshing taste and vitality-boosting properties."
msgstr "一颗爽脆的红苹果，以清新口感和恢复活力的效果闻名。"

msgid "A curved blade as swift and unyielding as the desert sun."
msgstr "一把弧形刀刃，像沙漠烈日一样迅疾而无情。"

msgid "A heavy blade crafted for sheer power and decisive strikes."
msgstr "为纯粹力量与致命一击打造的厚重刀刃。"

msgid "A key that has been hidden a long time ago, seems to open a fancy door."
msgstr "一把被藏了很久的钥匙，似乎能打开一扇华丽的门。"

msgid "A knife made from bones. Quite effective."
msgstr "用骨头制成的小刀，意外地很实用。"

msgid "A refreshing cactus drink."
msgstr "一杯清爽的仙人掌饮料。"

msgid "A rusty key found in the abandoned mine."
msgstr "在废弃矿坑中找到的一把生锈钥匙。"

msgid "A simple bottle filled with clear water."
msgstr "一个装满清水的简单瓶子。"

msgid "A simple bow attack, shoot one arrow at a time."
msgstr "基础弓箭攻击，一次射出一支箭。"

msgid "A stamped letter given for a specific quest."
msgstr "为特定任务准备的盖章信件。"

msgid "A tarnished key found in the snake pit."
msgstr "在蛇坑里找到的一把失去光泽的钥匙。"

msgid "A thin, soft and warm shirt."
msgstr "一件轻薄、柔软又保暖的上衣。"

msgid "An empty glass bottle, ready to be filled with whatever the world has to offer."
msgstr "一个空玻璃瓶，随时可以装进这个世界提供的一切。"

msgid "Classic trousers ornated with some fluffy fur."
msgstr "经典长裤，点缀着柔软的绒毛。"

msgid "Jeans with snake skin chaps."
msgstr "带有蛇皮护腿的牛仔裤。"

