msgid "Morph"
msgstr "变形"

msgid "Run"
msgstr "奔跑"

msgid "Cast a fire projectile, igniting enemies with intense heat and power."
msgstr "发射一枚火焰弹，以炽热高温点燃敌人。"

msgid "Cast a fire spray"
msgstr "喷射火焰"

msgid "Close combat attack."
msgstr "近距离战斗攻击。"

msgid "Heal yourself with a burst of restorative energy."
msgstr "用一股恢复能量治疗自己。"

msgid "Provide a light healing touch to allies or creatures."
msgstr "为盟友或生物提供轻度治疗。"

msgid "Releases a blue sonic wave that deals damage forward."
msgstr "释放一道向前造成伤害的蓝色音波。"

msgid "Toggle running to move faster at the cost of stamina."
msgstr "切换奔跑，以消耗体力为代价换取更快移动。"

msgid "Transform into your spirit form."
msgstr "变身为你的灵体形态。"

msgid "Unleash a mana-fueled attack, creating a focused circle of concentrated mana around you."
msgstr "释放一次由玛娜驱动的攻击，在你周围形成一圈集中的玛娜冲击。"

msgid "A Biting Thirst"
msgstr "噬人的干渴"

msgid "Grain in the desert"
msgstr "沙漠中的粮食"

msgid "Piou Slayer"
msgstr "皮欧猎手"

msgid "Sandstorm Mine Abandoned Treasure"
msgstr "沙暴矿坑的废弃宝藏"

msgid "Ship Alige Hide"
msgstr "阿莉热的藏身处"

msgid "Snake Pit Clue"
msgstr "蛇坑线索"

msgid "Snake Pit Thief"
msgstr "蛇坑盗贼"

msgid "Investigate a hidden bedroom deep within the Snake Pit, uncover the fate of a Tulimshar thief, solve his riddle, and recover the treasure he never reclaimed."
msgstr "调查蛇坑深处的一间隐藏卧室，揭开一名图利姆沙尔盗贼的命运，解开他的谜题，并取回他再也没能拿走的宝藏。"

msgid "Riskim the baker is waiting for a grain shipment marked with a blue Artis seal. Check the barrels at the docks."
msgstr "面包师里斯基姆正在等待一批印有蓝色阿尔缇斯封印的粮食。去码头检查那些木桶。"

